@page "/"

<PageTitle>SkiaSharp Extended - Blazor Demo</PageTitle>

<h1>SkiaSharp Extended Demos</h1>

<p>
    Welcome to the <strong>SkiaSharp.Extended</strong> Blazor demo app.
    Use the navigation menu to explore the core extended features:
</p>

<h4 class="text-muted mt-4 mb-3">EXTENDED</h4>

<div class="demo-list">
    <div class="card mb-3">
        <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">Shapes</h5>
            <p class="card-text">
                The rectangle and circle provided by SkiaSharp are very nice,
                but sometimes you need a bit more.
            </p>
            <a href="shapes" class="btn btn-primary">Open Demo</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card mb-3">
        <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">Path Interpolation</h5>
            <p class="card-text">
                There are also a few things that might be nice if we could
                interpolate from one path to another.
            </p>
            <a href="interpolation" class="btn btn-primary">Open Demo</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card mb-3">
        <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">BlurHash</h5>
            <p class="card-text">
                That time you wanted a compact representation of a placeholder
                for an image, but as a short data string.
            </p>
            <a href="blurhash" class="btn btn-primary">Open Demo</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card mb-3">
        <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">Pixel Comparer</h5>
            <p class="card-text">
                Compare two images pixel by pixel, see the difference mask,
                and get detailed error statistics.
            </p>
            <a href="pixelcomparer" class="btn btn-primary">Open Demo</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<h4 class="text-muted mt-4 mb-3">CONTROLS</h4>

<div class="demo-list">
    <div class="card mb-3">
        <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">Gestures</h5>
            <p class="card-text">
                Platform-agnostic gesture recognition for SkiaSharp surfaces.
                Pan, pinch, rotate, fling, double-tap zoom, and more.
            </p>
            <a href="gestures" class="btn btn-primary">Open Demo</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
